    <item>
      <title>Setting up a VPN on a Unifi USG</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/post/setting-up-unifi-vpn/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2019 08:58:07 -0600</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/post/setting-up-unifi-vpn/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Needed to set up a VPN on my Unifi&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;enable-the-radius-service&#34;&gt;Enable the radius service&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Settings -&amp;gt; Radius -&amp;gt; Server
Set a good secret&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;create-a-network&#34;&gt;Create a network&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Set the type to Remote User VPN
Specify a network for it&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;create-a-user&#34;&gt;Create a User&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can specify a VLAN for them here
Set tunnel type to L2TP
Set tunnel medium type to IPv4&lt;/p&gt;</description>
